    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "FROM: L. B. Nichols",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Title",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "unidentified \"flying object\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Great Meadows, New Jersey",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "March 12, 1957",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "SUBJECT: GREAT MEADOWS, NEW JERSEY",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "For record purposes, [REDACTED] (Great Meadows,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "New Jersey, telephone [REDACTED]) telephoned from his home at 12:52 p. m.,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "March 14, 1957, while I was tied up on another matter, and talked with Wick.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[REDACTED] age 56, is one of the original founders of [REDACTED] was",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "employed by Louis de Rochemont on our movie, \"House on 92nd Street,\" and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "he formerly was editor of [REDACTED]. He married [REDACTED] whom",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "he says is known to the Director. He has one arm.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "MYS",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "[REDACTED] said, to make a long story short, that he has run into",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "a situation which has to do with an unidentified flying object observed two days",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "ago in the Great Meadows vicinity. [REDACTED] said he had made a formal report",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "in writing to military authorities, as well as to two civilian groups interested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "in the affair. General Wedemeyer is connected with one of the latter groups.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "[REDACTED] said he is not satisfied that the \"intelligence\" he supplied to the military",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "is being handled properly, nor does he know to whom he should submit infor-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "mation and in what fashion. He said frankly he wanted an Agent to call upon",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "him so that the Agent could evaluate his information, although he said he well",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "knew \"flying saucers,\" etc., were not within the scope of the FBI's interest",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "nor jurisdiction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "(The attached news ticker from United Press reflects that in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "testimony before a House Appropriations Subcommittee, 2-19-57, Dr. Hugh",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Dryden, Director of the National Advisory Committee for Aeronautics, had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "flatly stated there is no such thing as a flying saucer. It was said too that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Air Force or some other authority should nail down the unidentified \"flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "objects\" and \"say it is pure fiction.\")",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "ACTION TAKEN:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "ENCLOSURE",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "While normally we would simply tell a caller that we have no",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
